name: What are the achievements of JECRC.

speech: Do you know JECRC is organizing JECRC Hackathon 1.O on 10 january 2018.
Do you know Dr. Vijay Singh Rathore, Prof. Dept. of CSE received “The Significant Contribution Award 2016” and “Active Participation Youth Award 2016” under CSI Service Awards at Coimbatore.
Do you know Shreyansh Pandey from 1st year ECE branch grabbed a Research Fellowship [Distance] from IISC Bangalore, which was initiated in academic year 2016-17 with a topic of “YOUTH PSYCHOLOGY”.
Aditi Parikh from 3rd Year CSE won first prize in the event escalade at IIT Guwahati.
